'''聖海倫斯'''（{{lang-en|St Helens}}）<ref name=Samuel>{{cite book | author=Lewis, Samuel (editor)| title=A Topographical Dictionary of England| publisher=Hedon - Helmington | year=1848 | pages=466–470 | isbn=0-8063-1508-3}}</ref><ref name=CivilParish>{{cite web|url=http://www.visionofbritain.org.uk/relationships.jsp;jsessionid=B05CA64B540F7307A5623FAFF310B5D5?u_id=10378825|title=Administrative unit: St Helens Civil Parish|author=University of Portsmouth|publisher=visionofbritain.org.uk|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100220010203/http://www.visionofbritain.org.uk/relationships.jsp|archivedate=2010-02-20}}</ref>是[[英國|英國]][[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[默西賽德郡|默西賽德郡]]的一座[[城市|城市]]，擁有超過十萬的人口。在歷史上屬蘭開夏郡。聖海倫斯曾經是一座工業都市，不過現在已經轉換為一座商業都市。

